data.description: 4 BEDROOMS + GAME ROOM + MEDIA ROOM! This home has it all and is ready to call it YOURS. Walk in to a High Ceiling Foyer, OPEN LIVING AREA, KITCHEN AND DINING AREA. SPACIOUS PRIMARY ROOM features a TRAY CEILING and view that overlooks the large back yard. At the top of the stairs is a game room with plenty of space for your gaming needs. To the left are double doors leading in to the media room which is prewired with surround sound and no windows for a perfect movie watching room. Three large secondary bedrooms and a secondary bathroom is between two of the bedrooms. The back yard has a nice porch area and has plenty of room for entertaining or just relaxing. Come soak up the sun in Audubon!  Almost New!  See the difference this home has to offer over other new homes close by.
